text: Sanne van der Werff (born 11 March 1998) is a Dutch korfball player. She is a member of PKC and the Netherlands national korfball team. Van der Werff is a player of the national team since 2021. With the national team she won the gold medal at the 2022 World Games in Birmingham, Alabama. ==Achievements== ===Club=== *Korfbal League champion, 1x (2021) * champion, 1x (2022) *, 1x (2021) *Best under-21 korfball player, 1x (2019) ===National team=== *World Games champion, 1x (2022) *European champion, 1x (2021) ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch korfball players Category:Sportspeople from South Holland Category:Sportswomen
